  "detailed_description": "<h1>Roadmap</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Updating roadmap. Coming soon!</p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Join our antihero on an antiquest to find beer in a post apocalypse wasteland!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The recent update v0.4.2.0 in July brings in a complete overhaul of the game, storyline, new maps, mechanics & more!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shoot, loot and talk your way through a landscape filled with raiders, mutants and original characters. Currently 2-4 hours of gameplay. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2459980/extras/e1db3bcf79b00b8139de3b7cabd9c39a.avif?t=1754979809\" width=616 height=256 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>RPG Lite</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An RPG focused on the story and environemnt of the WastePunk world. Meet NPCs and find out what's happening in the wasteland. <strong>Contains simplified RPG mechanics.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2459980/extras/76c6dec3c7001c3b3cccf404d36e668b.poster.avif?t=1754979809\" width=616 height=229 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2459980/extras/76c6dec3c7001c3b3cccf404d36e668b.webm?t=1754979809\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mega Deluxe Art Style!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Detailed, hand-crafted post-apocalyptic environments, created in a unique style, are waiting to fulfill your deepest post-apocalyptic desires!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2459980/extras/508d458a40531b1b954d617cc2c4cfba.poster.avif?t=1754979809\" width=616 height=215 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2459980/extras/508d458a40531b1b954d617cc2c4cfba.webm?t=1754979809\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Level Up and Get Ahead</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your hard earned cash and experience points to upgrade your arsenal!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2459980/extras/a0d5b3507537a5bead476070449ac437.poster.avif?t=1754979809\" width=616 height=229 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2459980/extras/a0d5b3507537a5bead476070449ac437.webm?t=1754979809\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Quests</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solve a small variety of quest to finally reach your goal.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Note: Early Access </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >At this point of time the game contains a storyline and all the features although the content is still incomplete. </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Join our antihero on an antiquest to find beer in a post apocalypse wasteland!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The recent update v0.4.2.0 in July brings in a complete overhaul of the game, storyline, new maps, mechanics & more!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shoot, loot and talk your way through a landscape filled with raiders, mutants and original characters. Currently 2-4 hours of gameplay. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2459980/extras/e1db3bcf79b00b8139de3b7cabd9c39a.avif?t=1754979809\" width=616 height=256 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>RPG Lite</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An RPG focused on the story and environemnt of the WastePunk world. Meet NPCs and find out what's happening in the wasteland. <strong>Contains simplified RPG mechanics.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2459980/extras/76c6dec3c7001c3b3cccf404d36e668b.poster.avif?t=1754979809\" width=616 height=229 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2459980/extras/76c6dec3c7001c3b3cccf404d36e668b.webm?t=1754979809\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mega Deluxe Art Style!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Detailed, hand-crafted post-apocalyptic environments, created in a unique style, are waiting to fulfill your deepest post-apocalyptic desires!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2459980/extras/508d458a40531b1b954d617cc2c4cfba.poster.avif?t=1754979809\" width=616 height=215 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2459980/extras/508d458a40531b1b954d617cc2c4cfba.webm?t=1754979809\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Level Up and Get Ahead</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your hard earned cash and experience points to upgrade your arsenal!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2459980/extras/a0d5b3507537a5bead476070449ac437.poster.avif?t=1754979809\" width=616 height=229 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2459980/extras/a0d5b3507537a5bead476070449ac437.webm?t=1754979809\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Quests</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solve a small variety of quest to finally reach your goal.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Note: Early Access </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >At this point of time the game contains a storyline and all the features although the content is still incomplete. </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
